[{"index":1,"title":"【贴图】生命——值得我们活着","content":"一滴水的存在,一朵花的存在,一粒沙的存在,&nbsp;\r<br>一切生命的存在,想一想都是那么美好.&nbsp;\r<br>","author":"简信","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.734cfd90.c0rLNkRTDp7Zcd5Bv5DoIg&fr=pb","date":"2006-07-03 15:36","ip":null,"old_image":"http://srflower.free.fr/makpix/worthlive/srh1-1.jpg","user_sign_image":null},{"index":2,"title":"回复：【贴图】生命——值得我们活着","content":"我们可以感受到这一切的存在,包括我们自己的存在.&nbsp;\r<br>生命给了我们一种状态--存在;若干形式--呼吸,行走,微笑......","author":"简信","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.734cfd90.c0rLNkRTDp7Zcd5Bv5DoIg&fr=pb","date":"2006-07-03 15:40","ip":null,"old_image":"http://srflower.free.fr/makpix/worthlive/srh1-2.jpg","user_sign_image":null},{"index":3,"title":"回复：【贴图】生命——值得我们活着","content":"当清晨或温柔或妩媚的阳光,暖暖撒在我们的身上,&nbsp;\r<br>是的,总有一面是阳光无法照射到的.可是你会因为另一侧小小的&nbsp;\r<br>阴影而感到不快乐吗?&nbsp;\r<br>你会心得,笑着说:&nbsp;&quot;不,这就是生活.我享受这一切.&quot;&nbsp;\r<br>生命值得我们活着.好好的活着,狠狠地活着,酸甜苦辣的活着...","author":"简信","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.734cfd90.c0rLNkRTDp7Zcd5Bv5DoIg&fr=pb","date":"2006-07-03 15:40","ip":null,"old_image":"http://srflower.free.fr/makpix/worthlive/srh1-8.jpg","user_sign_image":null},{"index":4,"title":"回复：【贴图】生命——值得我们活着","content":"每一个生命都是唯一,这是多么不可思议.是怎样的千辛万苦?&nbsp;\r<br>几世的恩怨情仇?是巧合还是注定?我们不得而知,唯有珍惜,&nbsp;\r<br>从开始的那一秒到离开的那一瞬......","author":"简信","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.734cfd90.c0rLNkRTDp7Zcd5Bv5DoIg&fr=pb","date":"2006-07-03 15:41","ip":null,"old_image":"http://srflower.free.fr/makpix/worthlive/srh2-7.jpg","user_sign_image":null},{"index":5,"title":"回复：【贴图】生命——值得我们活着","content":"许多美好,还未等我们经过,转瞬即逝.&nbsp;\r<br>错过多少并不重要,其中有多少是被放弃?","author":"简信","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.734cfd90.c0rLNkRTDp7Zcd5Bv5DoIg&fr=pb","date":"2006-07-03 15:41","ip":null,"old_image":"http://srflower.free.fr/makpix/worthlive/srh2-2.jpg","user_sign_image":null},{"index":6,"title":"回复：【贴图】生命——值得我们活着","content":"不,我们是唯一,或贫穷或富有,或幸福或悲伤,&nbsp;\r<br>或勤劳或懒惰,或放纵或矜持,或热烈或宁静.&nbsp;\r<br>或坚强或懦弱...是生活,是我们的生活.","author":"简信","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.734cfd90.c0rLNkRTDp7Zcd5Bv5DoIg&fr=pb","date":"2006-07-03 15:42","ip":null,"old_image":"http://srflower.free.fr/makpix/worthlive/srh2-6.jpg","user_sign_image":null},{"index":7,"title":"回复：【贴图】生命——值得我们活着","content":"不是每个决定都是正确,至少是我们自己的选择.&nbsp;\r<br>我们是自己生命的见证,这样还不够伟大吗?&nbsp;\r<br>当视觉的类同感逊色消磨着生活的画面,&nbsp;\r<br>我们的眼睛不再清澈,&nbsp;\r<br>伸出双手,在空中胡乱捕捉,&nbsp;\r<br>为什么,有的人在笑,有的人在哭.&nbsp;\r<br>有的人渐渐安静,有的人渐渐抓狂&nbsp;\r<br>.....","author":"简信","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.734cfd90.c0rLNkRTDp7Zcd5Bv5DoIg&fr=pb","date":"2006-07-03 15:43","ip":null,"old_image":"http://srflower.free.fr/makpix/worthlive/srh2-8.jpg","user_sign_image":null},{"index":8,"title":"回复：【贴图】生命——值得我们活着","content":"庆幸的是,生命对于我们是未知.电影的情节永远待续,&nbsp;\r<br>这会激发演员无限的潜力吗,你会为之兴奋?还是为之苦恼?&nbsp;\r<br>总是在收拾房间的时候,舍不得丢舍,每一样陪我们走过,&nbsp;\r<br>属于过我们的生命,都无法被抹掉,即使被遗忘,它也是不可缺少,&nbsp;\r<br>因为,一路走来,没有留白,一秒一秒,一步一步,直到静止,直到悬空...\u0018","author":"简信","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.734cfd90.c0rLNkRTDp7Zcd5Bv5DoIg&fr=pb","date":"2006-07-03 15:44","ip":null,"old_image":"http://srflower.free.fr/makpix/worthlive/srh3-4.jpg","user_sign_image":null},{"index":9,"title":"回复：【贴图】生命——值得我们活着","content":"-----------------------END-----------------------------","author":"简信","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.734cfd90.c0rLNkRTDp7Zcd5Bv5DoIg&fr=pb","date":"2006-07-03 15:44","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":10,"title":"回复：【贴图】生命——值得我们活着","content":"顶~~~~~~","author":"风铃≌摇摇","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.cfd1d03e.AMqAx4yImfXPR1yUv18nEg&fr=pb","date":"2006-07-03 16:38","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":11,"title":"回复：【贴图】生命——值得我们活着","content":"感觉好恬静啊~","author":"百度用户#7843130","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.14e7cee9.mGa0iWPh2LXGGOB0MR4GtA?t=1665373695&fr=pb","date":"